pullRequest.title: automl-beta: copy v1 samples to beta folder and update imports
pullRequest.bodyText:
Some beta samples haven't been merged to master and are on branches.
This PR takes the published V1 samples and copies them over to the beta folder for the products still in GA.
Partial fix for: #2011

commit.message: automl-beta: copy v1 samples to beta folder and update imports
